description:
A kind of "gatekeeper between the worlds"; her exact status is unknown. She appears human but might be a supernatural being.
Her name is taken from the manga but never mentioned in the anime.
She informs http://anidb.net/ch25713 [Gigelf Liqueur] that http://anidb.net/ch25712 [Ganossa Maximilian] is about to sabotage the http://anidb.net/ch25784 [Project Gaia].
name: Teres
